text:
Something you seek is
not of this world... but
above it!

Defeat the woman of
the air. It is to the
east you must go.
Gubasha Desert

text:
Come in, sit with me!
Warm yourself by the
fire! I know it can get

colder than Ganon's
heart up here, but I've
endured worse. Once,

when I was in the
Forest of Torian... er,
no, it was... it was the

Forest of Canvula! No,
no, it cannot be true,
for Canvula wood is

always hot, and did I
say... I did say it was
cold, right?

Well, then it was the
Forest of Torian!

text:
W... What do you want
with me? Uh, cannot
someone other worthy

help you? Erm, even if 
do help you, you cannot
for a moment believe

you shall defeat the
mighty Ganon... do you?

text:
I am called Myntoll, and
I know who you are.
Do you not grow bored

with your quest? I
certainly would.

You again? I suppose
you want Rupees or
information or

directions to a Shrine
or whatnot. Really, it
is all too dull!
